          "name": "Dark Chamber",
          "description": "This small chamber is dark for the most part, save for the few stray rays of reddish light that reach up from the room below. The floor is cold to the touch, and the walls flanking it on three sides tower upward into the darkness. To the east stands an enormous stone door that bears various sinister carvings.",
