          "description": "You stand at the end of a long stone table, upon which lay several tattered parchments. An unpleasant scent assaults your nostrils, and you notice the source, a platter of half eaten raw meat. The walls are decorated with carvings similar to those on the door to the west, and you notice a set of runes on the far wall. The room is bathed in a red glow produced by a swirling orb that is set in the center of the table.",
