          "description": "You experience a sharp jolt as you are thrust upon a sandy shore. The river bends to the south, where it disappears beneath a low rocky overhang. A faint cry sounds in the distance to the northeast, where a narrow passageway opens. As you move cautiously toward it, a brittle crunch sounds briefly beneath your feet.",
