          "description": "You stand in a small round room carved out of the surrounding rock, and notice that the ceiling here is quite a bit lower than that in the cavern you passed through. The floor is littered with fragments of brittle bone, stained brown with dried blood. Several large stones have been placed around a glowing orb in the center of the room. The remains of an animal carcass lay strewn about on the floor, and appear to have been partially eaten.",
